{"tid":1695763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（經濟攬炒）第3季食肆收益跌11.7%　沙士以來最大按年跌幅","createTime":"2019-11-05T23:46:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T00:47:29.000Z","uid":50457,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"816008e08b1adadae03f8ed8170c82d5890bf689","tid":1695763,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T23:46:24.000Z","msg":"政府統計處發表最新的食肆收益及購貨額臨時數字。今年第三季的食肆總收益價值的臨時估計為264億元，按年下跌11.7%，同期間食肆購貨總額的臨時估計為85億元，按年下跌10.9%，如扣除價格變動影響，食肆總收益以數量計按年跌13.6%。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n按食肆類別對比今年第三季與去年第三季數據，中式餐館的總收益以價值計及數量計分別下跌17.8%及19.7%；非中式餐館的總收益以價值計及數量計分別下跌13.3%及15.1%；快餐店的總收益以價值計及數量計分別上升2.2%及0.7%；酒吧的總收益以價值計及數量計分別下跌18.0%及18.6%；雜類飲食場所的總收益以價值計及數量計分別下跌2.0%及5.2%。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n而今年第三季與上季比較，經季節性調整的食肆總收益以價值計及數量計分別下跌10.6%及11.4%。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n政府發言人指出，食肆收益在第三季顯著惡化，錄得自2003年第二季沙士爆發以來最大的按年跌幅。食肆收益在第三季急跌，主要反映本地社會事件對餐飲業務構成的嚴重干擾，經濟狀況欠佳令消費情緒疲弱亦是原因之一，未來餐飲業在短期內仍然會面對相當大的壓力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2491071/%E7%AC%AC3%E5%AD%A3%E9%A3%9F%E8%82%86%E6%94%B6%E7%9B%8A%E8%B7%8C11.7-%E3%80%80%E6%B2%99%E5%A3%AB%E4%BB%A5%E4%BE%86%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E6%8C%89%E5%B9%B4%E8%B7%8C%E5%B9%85?mtc=20023\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2491071%2F%25E7%25AC%25AC3%25E5%25AD%25A3%25E9%25A3%259F%25E8%2582%2586%25E6%2594%25B6%25E7%259B%258A%25E8%25B7%258C11.7-%25E3%2580%2580%25E6%25B2%2599%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E4%25BE%2586%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%258C%2589%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25B7%258C%25E5%25B9%2585%3Fmtc%3D20023&d=YDk3w6YkG5F4GHIJWz3fGIaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=990c726b\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2491071/%E7%AC%AC3%E5%AD%A3%E9%A3%9F%E8%82%86%E6%94%B6%E7%9B%8A%E8%B7%8C11.7-%E3%80%80%E6%B2%99%E5%A3%AB%E4%BB%A5%E4%BE%86%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E6%8C%89%E5%B9%B4%E8%B7%8C%E5%B9%85?mtc=20023</a><br />\n<br />\n繼續維持低內部消費，罷紅藍買黃，目標下年失業率5.0<br />\n<br />\n只有拖散經濟政府先會聽人民說話"},{"pid":"23ad211eca7f439e06f650eb9dea310bb4c2dd5f","tid":1695763,"uid":74155,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T23:48:00.000Z","msg":"唔好太自滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e9453b8ca36a69a396fe91262db6433a1c9955e","tid":1695763,"uid":50457,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T23:49:21.000Z","msg":"堅持減少消費，每星期活動，經濟一死，就會有更多人上街<br />\n<br />\n總之有自由行的鬧區，就有活動"},{"pid":"ee541fca992ab265034fab3b40147b59fc7b6820","tid":1695763,"uid":63,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T23:50:18.000Z","msg":"樓又無 經濟發展又無份享受 不如攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19c22fbbbf76c8e5010bd507d024b6200ec75ecc","tid":1695763,"uid":50457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ee541fca992ab265034fab3b40147b59fc7b6820","tid":1695763,"uid":63,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T23:50:18.000Z","msg":"樓又無 經濟發展又無份享受 不如攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T23:51:58.000Z","msg":"香港市民初心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e2a6c0425375d984511b01ca49fb97d1a47b527","tid":1695763,"uid":259813,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T23:55:25.000Z","msg":"我怕驚賊打我，又怕冇車返屋企，唔敢出遠門同朋友仔食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29657a4a1d52a80fc76742bd3e4c16c00a2f7624","tid":1695763,"uid":2189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T23:57:27.000Z","msg":"周圍見到popo，<br />\n嚇到怕事藍絲縮曬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85eecdc8cbf23fae5112c3c252f4a5c1095b3f04","tid":1695763,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e2a6c0425375d984511b01ca49fb97d1a47b527","tid":1695763,"uid":259813,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"r